nodes.text: "Echo Five" was a female pilot who served in the Rebel Alliance during the Galactic Civil War. After the destruction of Alderaan, she served under the callsign Echo Five for Echo Squadron and participated in a battle at Fostar Haven, flying an X-wing. During the initial stages of the battle, she was killed when Echo Squadron had to fly under the Imperial II-class Star Destroyer Vigilance to get to the stranded Alderaanian refugee convoy.
"Echo Five" was a Rebel non-player character in the 2020 video game Star Wars: Squadrons.
